                            <p>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Note</hi>.—No interest can be allowed except in
                                accordance with the bond of indemnity which authorized interest on
                                the monthly advance payments made within the half-year Period. The
                                monthly installments of August 1, September 1 and October 1 were
                                paid October 1 and 10; hence interest is allowed on the amount of
                                said installments from date of payment to the end of the year. The
                                other payments in October are treated as payments of the monthly
                                installments of November 1 and December 1; hence interest is allowed
                                from November 1 and December 1, respectively: the dates the monthly
                                installments earn interest under the terms of the bond.</p>
